column2: The lands that formed the Anglian Eorldom of Lindesege have been reconquered from the Anglo-Saxons that once claimed the region for themselves.\n\nFrom this day on, the provinces around the former provincial capital of Lindum will once again belong 'de jure' to the High Lordship of Linnius and to the kingdom of Elmet. Any previous claim or birthright from the former Germanic rulers will no longer be recognized.
